      "writtenOn": "2026-05-13T13:25:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The guard now inspects next\u003d for already-authenticated users:\n\n  if (to.path \u003d\u003d\u003d \u0027/login\u0027 \u0026\u0026 store.getters[\u0027authentication/isLoggedIn\u0027]) {\n    if (isRedfishRedirectPath(to.query.next)) {\n      next(false);\n      window.location.assign(`${window.location.origin}${to.query.next}`);\n    } else {\n      next(\u0027/\u0027);\n    }\n    return;\n  }\n\nSafe Redfish paths trigger a full-page navigation via\nwindow.location.assign(); all other cases use next(\u0027/\u0027).",
